s watch events from the Kubernetes API server's watch stream. The `ListAndWatch` method (line 348) implements the main loop that maintains a watch connection to the API server and processes incoming events, updating a local cache store to keep it synchronized with server state.\n\nThe complete flow is: etcd MVCC store → serverWatchStream → Kubernetes Cacher (with watchCache and cacheWatcher distributing events) → Reflector (client-side watch handler) → local informer cache."
